KK
[[Image:Pedoteacher.jpg|thumb|right|He thought they were 18, HONEST!]]
'''KK''' is a pedo of the worst kind. He worked as a teacher at a pseudo-prestigious secondary school called [http://www.sfx.liverpool.sch.uk/ St Francis Xavier's College] which is in the [[England]]. And what's worse, he worked as the school choirmaster, meaning he got to see little kiddies dressed in frilly outfits. While it was known for a long time that Keith was a [[faggotry|faggy]] [[pedo]] among students, it took a little longer for the school administration to realize it. 

Not to be confused with [[KKK]].

==Rise to fagdom==

[http://icliverpool.icnetwork.co.uk/0100news/0100regionalnews/tm_objectid=16554425&method=full&siteid=50061&headline=choirmaster-child-porn-shock-name_page.html Keith made his initial successes with his choir of frilly schoolboys] who doubled as a [http://www.bbc.co.uk/liverpool/sport/2004/06/10/song_main.jpg dangerous gold-record wielding football squad]. However, his gold records were cut short in the fateful December of '05 when [http://icliverpool.icnetwork.co.uk/liverpooldailypost/news/regionalnews/tm_method=full%26objectid=18313966%26siteid=50061-name_page.html his girlfriend found pictures of naked boys and saw he'd been going on a kiddy pr0n site], and [[Police|The Bill]] broke into Keith's house and confiscated his computer, and then arrested him a little later when they found [[Child porn|kiddy pr0n]] on his computer.
[[Image:HomeAlone.jpg|thumb|left|The early days.]]

==In court==

In court, he kept [http://icliverpool.icnetwork.co.uk/0100news/0100regionalnews/tm_method=full%26objectid=16554425%26siteid=50061-name_page.html saying] and [http://icliverpool.icnetwork.co.uk/0100news/0100regionalnews/tm_method=full%26objectid=17089838%26siteid=50061-name_page.html saying] and [http://icliverpool.icnetwork.co.uk/liverpoolecho/news/echonews/tm_method=full%26objectid=18099428%26siteid=50061-name_page.html saying] that he was innocent, despite the fact that [[cops]] had [http://icliverpool.icnetwork.co.uk/liverpooldailypost/news/regionalnews/tm_method=full%26objectid=18104740%26siteid=50061-name_page.html found pictures of kiddies on his computer.]

Keith then said that [http://icliverpool.icnetwork.co.uk/liverpoolecho/news/echonews/tm_headline=community-work-for-child-porn-choirmaster%26method=full%26objectid=18300447%26page=2%26siteid=50061-name_page.html he was just trying the gay] and that he thought the kiddies were over 18. Right...

Eventually, when he was found [[Internet guilty|guilty]] of being a [[pedo]], he '''''still''''' said he was innocent and tried to appeal it, because he didn't want his name on the [[Megan's Law|sex offenders register]]. His defending lawyer added that [http://icliverpool.icnetwork.co.uk/liverpooldailypost/news/regionalnews/tm_method=full%26objectid=18104740%26siteid=50061-name_page.html he wouldn't go on kiddy pr0n sites because he had too much to lose]

==The Aftermath==

[[Image:keithknowles_bbc.jpg|thumb|right|He's all chubby now. Cute!]]
After Keith was found guilty of being a dirty pedo and got fired for it (he'd been suspended from the post until now 'cause the Boss thought he was innocent, or something), he was put on community service and given a supervision order. Boy, this country sure knows justice by letting kiddy fiddlers wander the streets don't it...

But Keithy insisted in appealing the sentence, because he doesn't want everyone to know he's a kiddy fiddler wherever he goes. Oh, and he's put on a bit of weight, too.

He has now apparently been cleared. I saw him in the pub a while ago with an old student. Clear and free, but for how long?

